<div id="review_3147907037" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3147907037" />
    <a title="Louise Savidge" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/108894214-louise-savidge"><img alt="Louise Savidge" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3147907037?book_show_action=true">Feb 03, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Louise Savidge" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Louise Savidge" href="/user/show/108894214-louise-savidge">Louise Savidge</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780099547075" href="/book/show/11464619-the-lost-books-of-the-odyssey">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3147907037" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10232002030795840891">Really enjoyed this. Felt as though I was swimming in and out of Odysseus’ thoughts at different points in the Odyssey. Loved the interpretation of Theseus and Ariadne. Not sure how readable it would be if you Weren’t familiar with The Odyssey.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


